'''拉里·费雷罗'''（{{lang-en|Larrie Ferreiro}}）是一位美国历史学家。

==生平==
出生于[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[长岛|长岛]]，2004年毕业于[[伦敦帝国学院|伦敦帝国学院]]，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mitpress.mit.edu/authors/larrie-d-ferreiro|title=Larrie D. Ferreiro|work=mit.edu|accessdate=28 January 2017|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202055104/https://mitpress.mit.edu/authors/larrie-d-ferreiro|dead-url=no}}</ref>先后任职于[[美国海军|美国海军]]、[[美国海岸警卫队|美国海岸警卫队]]及[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]。目前担任[[乔治梅森大学|乔治梅森大学]]教师。

==荣誉==
2017年凭借著作《友军》获得[[普利策历史奖|普利策历史奖]]决选名单。<ref>http://www.pulitzer.org/finalists/larrie-d-ferreiro {{Wayback|url=http://www.pulitzer.org/finalists/larrie-d-ferreiro |date=20201028063525 }} 2017</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pritzkermilitary.org/whats_on/pritzker-military-presents/larrie-ferreiro-brothers-arms-american-independence-and-men-france-and-spain-who-saved-it/|title=Larrie Ferreiro, Brothers at Arms: American Independence and the Men of France and Spain Who Saved It | Pritzker Military Museum & Library | Chicago|website=www.pritzkermilitary.org|access-date=2020-08-09|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117145556/https://www.pritzkermilitary.org/whats_on/pritzker-military-presents/larrie-ferreiro-brothers-arms-american-independence-and-men-france-and-spain-who-saved-it|dead-url=no}}</ref>

